                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/71246819/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-12-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">购于2015年秋京都百万遍旧书祭</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

